                <h1></h1>
                <p class="text-justify"><br>The theme of the camp can be chosen from the following 3 types: horseback riding, tennis and hot air balloon initiation. Participants can choose any type of camp, it is not mandatory that in a group of people all choose the same type of camp. Age categories: 7-11 years and 12-16 years. Accommodation is made in 4 * rooms, and 3 participants will be distributed in one room. Price:
- 1 day excursion camp - 250 lei / person, with entry from 9:00 in the morning on any day chosen from the grid presented above and exit in the evening at 22:30. The price includes 2 meals, 2 snacks, drinks throughout the day, many activities and wonderful surprises.
- 5-day camp - 285 euro / person, with entry on Monday morning at 8:00 and departure on Friday evening at 18:00. The price includes 3 meals, 2 snacks and drinks throughout the day, many activities and wonderful surprises.
- For groups of more than 15 people a 5% discount is offered on any option.
- For groups of over 30 people, a 10% discount is offered on any option, plus free attendance. Payment Terms:
- Advance 1 (for registration) - 15% of the total value;
- Advance 2 (within 60 days after registration) - 25% of the total value;
- Remaining Payment - 60% until 30 days before the start date;
- FULL payment - if the booking date is less than 30 days from the start date;
- The refund of the advances can be made until the latest at full payment. After paying the last installment, ie full payment, you can only change the names of the participants, but no money will be refunded. If you want you can separately opt for a cancellation insurance. This is something you should do individually with an insurance company. Method of payment: Cash, bank card, holiday voucher card, holiday vouchers / vouchers (on paper), bank transfer, cash deposit directly into the account, online payment by bank card via a secure link.<br><br><br></p>
